arduino pinout:

DISP_PWM_PIN 10 -- PB2
MENU_PIN 2 -- PD2
UP_PIN 9 -- PB1
DOWN_PIN 8 -- PB0
RELAY_PIN 13 -- PB5
TENS_FET 12 -- PB4
ONES_FET 11 -- PB3
(driven high, duh)
TEMP_SENSOR 3 -- PD3

BCD PINS

B0 -> 4 -- PD4
B1 -> 5 -- PD5
B2 -> 6 -- PD6
B3 -> 7 -- PD7

CHANGED RELAY PIN so programming won't interfere
NEW RELAY PIN -- PC3